title: Coast to Coast AM - Aug 02 2013 - Haunted Locations - Open Lines
description:
Date:	08-02-13
Host:	George Noory
Guests:	Rebecca F. Pittman, Open Lines
News segment guests: Lauren Weinstein, Dr. Peter Breggin, and Engelbert Humperdinck

Hours 3 & 4: Open Lines followed.
